while in custody.

179
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:11,444
You're smart enough
to know the CIA

180
00:20:11,535 --> 00:20:12,946
has big, wide, comfy cells

181
00:20:13,037 --> 00:20:15,742
with hot water,
cotton sheets, and TV.

182
00:20:15,831 --> 00:20:18,073
We also have cramped,
cold, little cells

183
00:20:18,167 --> 00:20:20,124
with a bare cot
and a hole in the floor.

184
00:20:20,211 --> 00:20:23,247
See, either way,
you're coming home with us.

185
00:20:23,339 --> 00:20:25,213
Where you live is up to you.

186
00:20:29,595 --> 00:20:32,762
There is no bypassing
the system.

187
00:20:32,848 --> 00:20:34,093
Okay, Cummings told you

188
