guards that patrol.

191
00:20:41,023 --> 00:20:42,221
We need to find some way in.

192
00:20:42,316 --> 00:20:44,356
The Doleac Agenda could mean
the end of The Covenant.

193
00:20:44,443 --> 00:20:46,685
