is comprised of three zones.

199
00:20:59,417 --> 00:21:00,911
You've got your
automated sentry guns,

200
00:21:01,001 --> 00:21:02,745
electrified zone,
and the big finish,

201
00:21:02,837 --> 00:21:04,497
motion-triggered acid spray.

202
00:21:04,588 --> 00:21:05,668
So how do we get through?

203
