tunnel, you toss it in.

209
00:21:19,562 --> 00:21:21,222
The guns will open fire,

210
00:21:21,313 --> 00:21:23,306
but the ball will keep
moving, which means the guns

211
00:21:23,399 --> 00:21:27,183
are gonna keep firing until
they're out of ammunition.

212
00:21:27,278 --> 00:21:28,902
Now you're
at the electrified zone.

213
00:21:28,988 --> 00:21:31,989
Cummings armed the tunnel
with 150,000 volts,

214
00:21:32,074 --> 00:21:33,866
which will be
a 15 on this metre.

215
00:21:33,951 --> 00:21:36,193
You want to
double-check it there.

216
00:21:36,287 --> 00:21:37,698
The Neoprene layer
you will be wearing

