255
00:24:33,923 --> 00:24:36,378
I'm sorry you came so far,
Dr. Barnett.

256
00:24:39,220 --> 00:24:42,505
I can stay as long as it takes.

257
00:24:42,598 --> 00:24:43,843
We can just sit here

258
