I keep secrets.

442
00:36:31,390 --> 00:36:32,968
I divulge only what I must

443
00:36:33,059 --> 00:36:35,846
in order to elicit
the reaction I need.

444
00:36:35,936 --> 00:36:41,144
That skill, in part,
is why I'm still alive.

445
00:36:43,486 --> 00:36:44,565
One of those secrets

446
00:36:44,653 --> 00:36:47,987
