I know, isn't it?

481
00:39:25,731 --> 00:39:27,640
So, what do you suppose
we do about that?

482
00:39:30,736 --> 00:39:32,444
The fact that you murdered
our cell leaders.

483
00:39:32,530 --> 00:39:34,190
I presume you're smart enough
to know

484
00:39:34,281 --> 00:39:38,575
that I was acting in
The Covenant's best interest.

485
00:39:39,829 --> 00:39:43,245
